snippet.title: No More Room in Hell 2  - Game Overview Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2024
snippet.description:
Learn all about new horror co-op game sequel, No More Room in Hell 2 in this quick overview with the game's developers. Brave eight-player co-op and venture into the terrifying darkness of zombie-infested zones, but beware because permadeath may lurk around the next corner.

No More Room in Hell 2 is coming to PC.

#IGN #Gaming #NoMoreRoominHell
